{
  "arquivo": "op_02_01",
  "total": 63,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, sorry to have kept you waiting.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Ooh?\\nWhy are you here, Futaro-kun?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Why? I mean%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Oh! Did you perhaps come to the wrong place?\\nYou didn't listen carefully to what Itsuki-chan said,\\ndid you? You're hopeless.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Ichika.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Or did you confess to someone else already?\\nKnowing you, you're probably thinking\\nof meeting everyone, just to be safe.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ichika!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "...What?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I didn't come here by mistake.\\nI came to see you, Ichika.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "What are you talking about?\\nThat doesn't make any sense.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Did you mistake me for someone else, after all?\\nDon't try to weirdly cover it up.\\nLook, I'll guide you!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "So? Who do you want to see?\\nNino's in our classroom%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "ICHIKA!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I'll say it once again.\\nI came here to see you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I like you, Ichika.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Oh come on, what are you saying?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What do you mean?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I don't get it! I don't get it at all!\\nWhy me?! Why?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "You're crazy, Futaro-kun!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?\\nI'm crazy, you say?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Okay, then.\\nLet me explain it to you so that you can understand.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Explain what?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "What I like about you is obvious, isn't it?\\nSo that you can feel that I'm not crazy,\\nI'll take my time and tell you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Huh...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I've always watched you trying to be strong\\nfor your dreams and your own self.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You're always ahead of the game.\\nI thought, I wanted to catch up to you\\nso I could be with you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Also, I know the weak side of you\\nthat pushes yourself too hard, corners yourself.\\nSo%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "So, you'd better stop.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "You said I want to be strong for myself,\\nbut I just can't. I'm weaker, so I have to be\\nmore cunning than everyone else.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I'll only make you unhappy.\\nSo, you'd better stop, I say.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Don't underestimate me, Ichika.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Huh...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I don't really know what you're thinking to say,\\nor whether you're going to make me unhappy or not.\\nI don't know what the future holds!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But you don't have to worry about anything.\\nBecause I'll be able to heal your anxieties.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Then there won't be any problems, right?\\nDon't you agree?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "That's a pushy argument...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ichika.\\nLet me hear how you feel right now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "It's okay for me to love you, isn't it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I think I've caused you so much pain.\\nI'm really sorry.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "No...that's...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It's true, isn't it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "That's...not fair...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "You're right.\\nBut I won't make you cry like this anymore.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "This is completely different from before.\\nThese are tears of joy.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Is that so?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "Futaro-kun.\\nI love you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Ichika",
      "texto_en": "I've always loved you...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    }
  ]
}